examples.en: Most house plants require regular watering.
We helped the gardener in watering his flowers.
My eyes were watering as I chopped the onions.
Camels are accustomed to go several days without watering.
It is now the most fashionable watering place on the coast.
The lawn needs a great deal of watering.
Without endless watering, these fields will quickly return to desert.
Die-hard fans gathered at the local watering place to watch the Super Bowl.
